          <div class="text-blue-200 text-sm mt-1">Years Experience</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1D4ED8] mb-4">Winning NFL Betting Tips From the Pros</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#EF4444] mx-auto"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Whether you're a beginner or seasoned bettor, these proven tips will elevate your game to professional levels.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Essential Betting Strategies</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-l-4 border-[#1D4ED8] transition-transform hover:translate-x-2">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Line Shopping is Crucial</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>Always compare odds across multiple sportsbooks</li>
                <li>Even small line differences can significantly impact long-term profitability</li>
                <li>Use odds comparison tools to find the best value</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-l-4 border-[#EF4444] transition-transform hover:translate-x-2">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Bankroll Management Rules</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>Never risk more than 1-5% of your total bankroll on a single bet</li>
                <li>Set weekly and monthly loss limits</li>
                <li>Track every wager to identify winning patterns</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1D4ED8] to-[#3B82F6] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white shadow-xl">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üèÜ</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Advanced Betting Insights</h3>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl italic border-l-4 border-[#EF4444] pl-6 py-4 bg-white/10 rounded-r-lg">
            Information is the most valuable currency in sports betting.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
            <div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4 inline-flex items-center">
              <span class="mr-3">üí°</span>
              <span class="font-medium">Professional Bettor Tip</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Weather Impact Section -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">
        <div class="md:flex">
          <div class="md:w-2/5 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1D4ED8] to-[#2563EB] p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Weather Impact Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
              Environmental conditions can dramatically shift game outcomes and betting lines.
            </p>
