                <div class="text-3xl mb-2">‚ùÑÔ∏è</div>
                <div class="text-sm">Snow/Cold</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-3/5 p-8">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Key Factors to Monitor:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-[#EF4444] rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-xs">‚úì</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Field Conditions</h5>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Wet surfaces favor defensive teams and reduce scoring potential</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-[#EF4444] rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-xs">‚úì</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Passing Game Impact</h5>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Strong winds can limit aerial attacks, shifting game plans to ground game</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-[#EF4444] rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-xs">‚úì</span>
